#: ping/ping_common.c:49
#, c-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"Usage\n"
"  ping [options] <destination>\n"
"\n"
"Options:\n"
"  <destination>      DNS name or IP address\n"
"  -3                 RTT precision (do not round up the result time)\n"
"  -a                 use audible ping\n"
"  -A                 use adaptive ping\n"
"  -B                 sticky source address\n"
"  -c <count>         stop after <count> replies\n"
"  -C                 call connect() syscall on socket creation\n"
"  -D                 print timestamps\n"
"  -d                 use SO_DEBUG socket option\n"
"  -e <identifier>    define identifier for ping session, default is random "
"for\n"
"                     SOCK_RAW and kernel defined for SOCK_DGRAM\n"
"                     Imply using SOCK_RAW (for IPv4 only for identifier 0)\n"
"  -f                 flood ping\n"
"  -h                 print help and exit\n"
"  -H                 force reverse DNS name resolution (useful for numeric\n"
"                     destinations or for -f), override -n\n"
"  -I <interface>     either interface name or address\n"
"  -i <interval>      seconds between sending each packet\n"
"  -j                 JSON output (experimental)\n"
"  -L                 suppress loopback of multicast packets\n"
"  -l <preload>       send <preload> number of packages while waiting "
"replies\n"
"  -m <mark>          tag the packets going out\n"
"  -M <pmtud opt>     define path MTU discovery, can be one of <do|dont|want|"
"probe>\n"
"  -n                 no reverse DNS name resolution, override -H\n"
"  -O                 report outstanding replies\n"
"  -p <pattern>       contents of padding byte\n"
"  -q                 quiet output\n"
"  -Q <tclass>        use quality of service <tclass> bits\n"
"  -s <size>          use <size> as number of data bytes to be sent\n"
"  -S <size>          use <size> as SO_SNDBUF socket option value\n"
"  -t <ttl>           define time to live\n"
"  -U                 print user-to-user latency\n"
"  -v                 verbose output\n"
"  -V                 print version and exit\n"
"  -w <deadline>      reply wait <deadline> in seconds\n"
"  -W <timeout>       time to wait for response\n"
"\n"
"IPv4 options:\n"
"  -4                 use IPv4\n"
"  -b                 allow pinging broadcast\n"
"  -R                 record route\n"
"  -T <timestamp>     define timestamp, can be one of <tsonly|tsandaddr|"
"tsprespec>\n"
"\n"
"IPv6 options:\n"
"  -6                 use IPv6\n"
"  -F <flowlabel>     define flow label, default is random\n"
"  -N <nodeinfo opt>  use IPv6 node info query, try <help> as argument\n"
"\n"
"For more details see ping(8).\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"ວິທີໃຊ້\n"
"  ping [ຕົວເລືອກ] <ປາຍທາງ>\n"
"\n"
"ຕົວເລືອກ:\n"
"  <ປາຍທາງ>           ຊື່ DNS ຫຼື ທີ່ຢູ່ IP\n"
"  -3                 ຄວາມລະອຽດ RTT (ບໍ່ປັດເສດເວລາຜົນລັດ)\n"
"  -a                 ໃຊ້ສຽງເຕືອນ ping\n"
"  -A                 ໃຊ້ adaptive ping\n"
"  -B                 ບັງຄັບໃຊ້ທີ່ຢູ່ຕົ້ນທາງເດີມ\n"
"  -c <ຈຳນວນ>         ຢຸດຫຼັງຈາກໄດ້ຮັບການຕອບກັບຄົບ <ຈຳນວນ> ຄັ້ງ\n"
"  -C                 ເອີ້ນໃຊ້ connect() syscall ເມື່ອສ້າງ socket\n"
"  -D                 ສະແດງ timestamps\n"
"  -d                 ໃຊ້ຕົວເລືອກ socket SO_DEBUG\n"
"  -e <ຕົວລະບຸ>        ກຳນົດຕົວລະບຸສຳລັບ ping session, ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນແບບສຸ່ມສຳລັບ\n"
"                     SOCK_RAW ແລະ ກຳນົດໂດຍເຄີເນລສຳລັບ SOCK_DGRAM\n"
"                     ໝາຍເຖິງການໃຊ້ SOCK_RAW (ສຳລັບ IPv4 ທີ່ມີຕົວລະບຸ 0 ເທົ່ານັ້ນ)\n"
"  -f                 flood ping\n"
"  -h                 ສະແດງການຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອແລ້ວອອກ\n"
"  -H                 ບັງຄັບການແກ້ໄຂຊື່ reverse DNS (ມີປະໂຫຍດສຳລັບປາຍທາງທີ່ເປັນ\n"
"                     ຕົວເລກ ຫຼື ສຳລັບ -f), ແທນທີ່ -n\n"
"  -I <ອິນເຕີເຟສ>     ຊື່ອິນເຕີເຟສ ຫຼື ທີ່ຢູ່\n"
"  -i <ຊ່ວງເວລາ>      ວິນາທີລະຫວ່າງການສົ່ງແຕ່ລະແພັກເກັດ\n"
"  -j                 JSON output (ທົດລອງ)\n"
"  -L                 ລະງັບ loopback ຂອງແພັກເກັດ multicast\n"
"  -l <preload>       ສົ່ງແພັກເກັດຈຳນວນ <preload> ໃນຂະນະທີ່ລໍຖ້າການຕອບກັບ\n"
"  -m <mark>          ຕິດແທັກແພັກເກັດຂາອອກ\n"
"  -M <pmtud opt>     ກຳນົດ path MTU discovery, ສາມາດເປັນ <do|dont|want|probe>\n"
"  -n                 ບໍ່ມີການແກ້ໄຂຊື່ reverse DNS, ແທນທີ່ -H\n"
"  -O                 ລາຍງານການຕອບກັບທີ່ຍັງຄ້າງຢູ່\n"
"  -p <pattern>       ເນື້ອໃນຂອງ padding byte\n"
"  -q                 ໂໝດງຽບ\n"
"  -Q <tclass>        ໃຊ້ quality of service <tclass> bits\n"
"  -s <ຂະໜາດ>         ໃຊ້ <ຂະໜາດ> ເປັນຈຳນວນໄບທ໌ຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ຈະສົ່ງ\n"
"  -S <ຂະໜາດ>         ໃຊ້ <ຂະໜາດ> ເປັນຄ່າຕົວເລືອກ socket SO_SNDBUF\n"
"  -t <ttl>           ກຳນົດ time to live\n"
"  -U                 ສະແດງ latency ລະຫວ່າງຜູ້ໃຊ້ (user-to-user)\n"
"  -v                 ສະແດງລາຍລະອຽດການເຮັດວຽກ\n"
"  -V                 ສະແດງເວີຊັນແລ້ວອອກ\n"
"  -w <ກຳນົດເວລາ>      ເວລາລໍຖ້າການຕອບກັບ <ກຳນົດເວລາ> ເປັນວິນາທີ\n"
"  -W <ເວລາລໍຖ້າ>      ເວລາທີ່ຈະລໍຖ້າການຕອບສະໜອງ\n"
"\n"
"ຕົວເລືອກ IPv4:\n"
"  -4                 ໃຊ້ IPv4\n"
"  -b                 ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ ping ແບບ broadcast\n"
"  -R                 ບັນທຶກເສັ້ນທາງ (record route)\n"
"  -T <timestamp>     ກຳນົດ timestamp, ສາມາດເປັນ <tsonly|tsandaddr|tsprespec>\n"
"\n"
"ຕົວເລືອກ IPv6:\n"
"  -6                 ໃຊ້ IPv6\n"
"  -F <flowlabel>     ກຳນົດ flow label, ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນແບບສຸ່ມ\n"
"  -N <nodeinfo opt>  ໃຊ້ IPv6 node info query, ລອງໃຊ້ <help> ເປັນອາກິວເມັນ\n"
"\n"
"ສຳລັບລາຍລະອຽດເພີ່ມເຕີມ ເບິ່ງໄດ້ທີ່ ping(8).\n"

